[I] Meld visual diff and merge tool

[T] You can compare two or three files and edit them in place (diffs update
[T] dynamically). You can compare two or three folders and launch file comparisons.
[T] You can browse and view a working copy from popular version control systems
[T] such such as CVS, Subversion, Bazaar-ng and Mercurial.

[U] https://meld.sf.net

[A] Stephen Kennedy <stevek@gnome.org>
[M] René Rebe <rene@exactco.de>

